Delete reactions

Source: R/model_building.R

deleteReaction.Rd

deleteReaction deletes reactions.

deleteReaction(key, model = getCurrentModel())

Arguments

key

reaction keys
model

a model object

Details

Deletion quietly works recursively (deletes all connected entities) to prevent invalid model states.

See also

Other reaction functions: clearCustomKineticFunctions, deleteKineticFunction, entity_finders, getParameterReferences, getParameters, getReactionMappings, getReactionReferences, getReactions, getValidReactionFunctions, newKineticFunction, newReaction, setParameters, setReactionFunction, setReactionMappings, setReactions
